Business Sales Performance Analytics
Task Overview

This project focuses on analyzing business sales data to identify revenue trends, top-selling products, high-performing categories, and regional sales performance.

Objectives
Analyze overall sales performance
Identify top-selling products
Evaluate category-wise revenue
Compare regional performance
Generate actionable business insights
Tools Used
Microsoft Excel
Data Visualization Dashboard
Key Insights
Identified sales trends across different periods
Highlighted top-performing products and categories
Analyzed regional sales distribution
Provided recommendations for improving business performance
Deliverables
Sales Performance Dashboard
Analysis Report
Business Recommendations
Internship

Future Interns – Data Science & Analytics
